title: United Kingdom Imports - Photographic Or Cinematographic Products
description: Imports - Photographic Or Cinematographic Products in the United Kingdom decreased to 26.40 GBP Million in September from 27.70 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports - Photographic Or Cinematographic Products in the United Kingdom averaged 42.53 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 107.99 GBP Million in March of 2000 and a record low of 14.09 GBP Million in April of 2020. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Photographic Or Cinematographic Produc.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
